enc_tcl_report...der_with_value(25.10)  enc_tcl_report...der_with_value(25.10)

Name
       enc_tcl_report_header_with_value

Syntax
        enc_tcl_report_header_with_value {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: false

       When set to true, prints the Tcl variable value in the report header.

       Example

       In  the following example, tcl_report_header_with_value is set to true,
       the report shows the value, myct, set for the variable  in  the  report
       header.

       @[DEV]innovus 16> l {set enc_tcl_report_header_with_value 1}

       1

       @[DEV]innovus 17> report_analysis_coverage -check_type $myct

